column2: SELECT     s.specObjID,s.bestObjID,s.targetObjID,    s.ra, s.dec,s.mjd,    s.spectroFlux_u,s.spectroFlux_g,s.spectroFlux_r,    s.spectroFlux_i,s.spectroFlux_z,    s.spectroSynFlux_u,s.spectroSynFlux_g,s.spectroSynFlux_r,    s.spectroSynFlux_i,s.spectroSynFlux_z,    m.specObjID,m.ra,m.dec,    m.psfMag_u,  m.psfMag_g,  m.psfMag_r,  m.psfMag_i,    m.psfMag_z,  m.fiberMag_u,m.fiberMag_g,m.fiberMag_r,    m.fiberMag_i,m.fiberMag_z,s.sourceType,m.type   s.mjd as smjd, m.mjd as pmjd  INTO mydb.spec_#_galaxy_#  FROM SpecObjAll as s    JOIN SpecPhotoAll as m ON s.SpecObjID=m.SpecObjID  Where s.dec < #    And s.sourceType=&&&   And s.mjd > #
